TextEng: I'll pass. I'm not looking for trouble.
Text: 사양할게. 괜히 분란 일으킬 생각은 없어.

TextEng: I'm just looking for information. I'll gladly pay.
Text: 난 정보만 찾는 거야. 기꺼이 대가를 치르지.

TextEng: I'll match you drink for drink, no problem!
Text: 잔 대 잔으로 맞춰 주지! 문제없어!

TextEng: Me match you drinking! No problem!
Text: 나도 술 맞춰 마실래! 문제 없어!

TextEng: Me just want information. Me pay.
What is going on in here?
Thanks for your oh so important approval.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Not long. I replaced a plague victim.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 오래 안 됐어. 역병 희생자 대신 들어왔지.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Not long. Me replace plague-dead guy.
Text: <StartCheck>[거짓말]</Start> 오래 안 됐어. 나 역병으로 죽은 사람 대신 왔어.

TextEng: I'm just looking for information. That's all.
Text: 난 정보만 찾고 있어. 그게 전부야.

TextEng: I'm no Bloodsailor. I'm acting as a city guard.
Text: 나는 핏빛 항해자가 아니야. 지금은 도시 경비대 소속으로 일하고 있어.

TextEng: Me not Bloodsailor. Me here as city guard.
Text: 나 핏빛 항해자 아냐. 나 여기 도시 경비대로 왔어.

TextEng: Thanks. Maybe I'll just sit down for a bit, now.
Urp. Thanks. Maybe me sit for a bit now.
Text: 꺽. 고마워. 나도 잠깐 앉아 있을게.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> You and me! Let's do it!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> That right! You and me, drink it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> I am just fine! Swig it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> You're not stopping are you? Swig it!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> No stop yet, you! Swig it!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Bah! Nothing but water! Tip it back!
<StartCheck>[Constitution]</Start> Through the lips and over the gums!
Why are you here? What do you do?
Text: 여긴 왜 있지? 무슨 일을 하지?

TextEng: Why you here? What do you do?
Text: 너 왜 여기 있어? 무슨 일 해?
